### config file for realtime inputs

# how often to turn on heatbath trajectory mode
mode_interval 500

# how many trajectories during trajectory mode (fixed initial configuration)
n_traj 5

# how often to perform measurements in trajectory mode
interval 1

## min and max values of multicanonical order parameter in a trajectory
## trajectory is considered complete if the order param crosses min or max
min 0.10
max 0.90

